    <div class="about-row">
        <div class="about-column" style="width:100%">
            <p><b class="about-p">Skills</b></p>
            <p class="about-p">
                Here are the tools, frameworks, libraries, and coding languages
                Kalen has worked with, sorted by the time he last worked with
                them.
                <br />
                <div class="column pcol">
                    <b>Past Year</b>
                    <hr />
                    <div id="recent-skills"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="column pcol">
                    <b>1-2 Years Ago</b>
                    <hr />
                    <div id="whileago-skills"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="column pcol">
